		)
		(uuid "cfe27cba-3607-44a1-a449-5d0f36aa3e61")
	)
	(text "POWER:\n  ESP32 powered from 5V_SYS ONLY - never directly from LiPo\n  Charging and actuation MUTUALLY EXCLUSIVE\n  Firmware disables STEPPER_ENN on USB/charge detect\n\nLAYOUT (single-layer PCB - jumpers allowed):\n  Zone A (LEFT):   LiPo, TP4056, XL6009, bulk caps\n  Zone B (CENTRE): TMC2209, motor output traces\n  Zone C (RIGHT):  ESP32, FSR, OLED - farthest from boost\n  NEVER route motor return current through analog ground\n  Trunk+branch ground topology (battery-neg = origin)\n\nTRACE WIDTHS:\n  Power/GND: 1.5-2.0mm   Motor: 0.8-1.2mm\n  Digital: 0.25-0.4mm    Analog/I2C: 0.25-0.4mm\n\nFIRMWARE RULES:\n  Never start all 3 motors simultaneously (stagger 50-100ms)\n  Sample FSR only when motors idle or use median filter x5\n  OLED update rate <= 10Hz during actuation\n  Expose PDN_UART and DIAG pads per TMC2209\n  USB port on ESP32 and TP4056 must remain accessible"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 110.49 246.38 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1 1)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "e0492219-99b1-4080-aa57-44118eded0fb")
	)
